headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Triple Rewards on Lamar Contact Missions
content: Lamar Davis is one of Los Santos’ most infamous stick-up artists — he’s always looking for a score, and he doesn’t care if he has to crack a couple unsuspecting eggs to make an omelet. Help Lamar out by giving him a call on his iFruit and earn 3X the usual GTA$ and RP all week long.
